snippet.textDisplay:
No offense to everyone who all liked this song, just coming from a very different thought process, there was a reason that why Coke Studio India dint work earlier and Pakistan is at season 14, Coke Studio Bangla is at season 2 which started just last year, I think we are repeating the mistake.
The arrangements are somehow not synching and complementing each other for me, Sarod, there was a sarod playing and I couldn't feel it's impact, Ravi Kishan and Maithili could have been in a duet then the rap could blend in, something's just not right. 🤷‍♀️
Or maybe this season will piggyback on the reels generation and still manage to garner views and popularity, but that dsnt have longevity and loyal audience.
